snippet: Ivory Latta scored 14 points and hit clutch shots in all three overtime sessions, and the Washington Mystics survived 31 turnovers for a 92-84 victory at home over the Los Angeles Sparks.
abstract: Washington Mystics beat Los Angeles Sparks, 92-84; other WNBA news noted.
